Class FragmentKey2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.knime.mmp.FragmentKey2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FragmentKey2>

    public class FragmentKey2
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<FragmentKey2>
    A simple class to hold the fragment key as an ArrayList, which is then sorted and concatenated to a multicomponent SMILES
    Author:
    s.roughley <knime@vernalis.com>
